reviewText: Lists DVD FORMAT BUT IT IS NOT! want a refund. Thought I was buying DVD as stated on the site.
Very disappointed! Movie would not work...said it was wrong region
VERY UNHAPPY!!! Region not disclosed in description so will not play in the U.S.A.
Waited way longer than usual. Once I got it, looked it over. Looked brand new. Threw the packaging away accidentally. NONE of the 3 discs worked. NOT happy. Now I'm just stuck with it.
